{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs36 Oscilloscope with beat retrigger\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 This is exactly the same as the default Cockos oscilloscope meter that comes with Reaper, but with an additional retrigger mode called "beat." This stabilizes the oscilloscope such that the far right edge is always the last sample of the beat that just finished. It is especially useful for designing EDM kick drums and observing kick/bass phase interaction patterns in real-time. Be sure to zoom correctly so that you can see the entire beat in the scope, as the initial zoom setting may not capture it.\par}
}

