{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Blipper - Tone generator, blip generator, periodic passthrough plugin.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Blipper is created for testing purposes. You can generate tuned sine tones from a wide range of frequencies/keys, and adjust them to be periodicly cut with or without a fade. Or instead of the tone you can pass through whatever is playing on the track already. You can also set a full passthrough volume to skip the blipping altogether.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 The plugin was created to test and measure compressor and reverb times and responses.\par}
